      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 19:12:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果美国撤资法案成为法律，TikTok 计划全面法律斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/tiktok-plans-full-legal-fight-if-us-divestment-bill-becomes-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，如果针对该应用程序的美国最新立法成为法律，TikTok 打算在考虑从中国母公司字节跳动有限公司进行任何形式的剥离之前，先排除所有法律挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/tiktok-plans-full-legal-fight-if-us-divestment-bill-becomes-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 18:30:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院即将进行撤资投票，TikTok 聚焦参议院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/tiktok-focuses-on-senate-as-house-barrels-toward-divestment-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TikTok 首席执行官 Shou Chew 周二前往国会山游说反对一项法案，该法案将迫使该应用程序的中国母公司出售该应用程序，否则将在美国面临禁令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/tiktok-focuses-on-senate-as-house-barrels-toward-divestment-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 17:57:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
